{"tid":1892110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：疫情或令失業率升至4%至5%","createTime":"2020-02-22T10:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:23:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1f61c8792b8e69091960612bee87a3804403ca","tid":1892110,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1510133_1_L_20200222123444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1510133_1_L_20200222123444.jpg&h=2073f2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光預期，本港失業率有機會升至4%至5%。<br />\n<br />\n他期望，300億元防疫抗疫基金可避免企業疫情期間倒閉，保留員工。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又指，如果要為各行各業設計支援方案，需時太長，所以先支援部分去年起已受衝擊行業，包括飲食、零售及旅遊業。"},{"pid":"53295e79651470736007e4373fbeff10f421f8bd","tid":1892110,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好重要！重整心態！唔想運動就咁完既請入去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得抗爭冷卻，係因為你地嘅心態好有問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0058a25d1d92bc402830af86d0fe3f6f5b6604e9","tid":1892110,"uid":329324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc1f61c8792b8e69091960612bee87a3804403ca","tid":1892110,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1510133_1_L_20200222123444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1510133_1_L_20200222123444.jpg&h=2073f2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光預期，本港失業率有機會升至4%至5%。